---
title: Quick Honey and Garlic Chicken Stew with Mash and Green Beans
description: Made with chicken stock for an intense boost of flavour, garlic and honey, our stew is fast and simple and tastes unbelievable. Paired with creamy, silky mashed potato, this is comfort food of the highest order.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/quick-honey-and-garlic-chicken-stew-fe7ac2ce-34d5b84c.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/quick-honey-and-garlic-chicken-stew-5dd7dabf6a1b2178a46c528f-80a8c526.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/quick-honey-and-garlic-chicken-stew-5dd7dabf6a1b2178a46c528f
author: Mimi Morley
servings: 2
course: main course
time required: 20 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 413 kcal
  fat: 3 g
  saturated fat: 1 g
  carbohydrates: 55 g
